CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 27, 1954, pg. 13 reads: "The Glamorous Cotillion - Scenes from the third annual debutante Cotillion given by Pittsburgh AKAs include...Far right: Mrs. Paul F. Jones and Alexander J. Allen walk to the podium where Mr. Allen acted as emcee and Mrs. Jones presented the debs..."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Paul F. Jones and Alexander Allen, walking in Syria Mosque during the Alpha Kappa Alpha's 1954 Cotillion
